 Willow 分享异想天开的新单曲“Big Feelings”并宣布专辑“Empathogen” https://www.nme.com/news/music/willow-shares-whimsical-new-single-big-feelings-and-announces-album-empathogen-3618188?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=willow-shares-whimsical-新单曲大感受并宣布专辑 EmpathogenAnagricel Duran Mon, 15 Apr 2024 21:20:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3618188 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威洛·史密斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她的第六张录音室专辑还与乔恩·巴蒂斯特和圣文森特合作</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/willow-shares-whimsical-new-single-big-feelings-and-announces-album-empathogen-3618188">Willow 分享了异想天开的新单曲“Big Feelings”，并宣布专辑“Empathogen”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威洛·史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Willow-Smith_2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/willow">Willow</a>分享了她异想天开的新单曲“Big Feelings”，并宣布了她的新专辑“Empathogen”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/willow-cover-interview-2021-lately-i-feel-everything-3109417"><em>NME</em>大读物 – Willow：“人类从来不善于接受人与人之间的差异”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌以爵士乐钢琴连复段开始，随后是震撼的底鼓。 <em>“我有如此强烈的感情/无法在没有声音的情况下将它们关闭/我有如此强烈的感情/无法将它们关闭或让它们出去，”</em>她在异想天开的节奏中唱道。</p><p>在一份声明（Per <a href="https://www.stereoboard.com/content/view/243553/9" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Stereoboard</em></a> ）中谈到这首歌时，Willow 说道：“这首歌的钢琴部分是如此密集和不和谐，但也有黑暗的美丽。我在一周内写了《bigfeeling s》，当时我正在接受自己的情绪模式，而我之前并不知道这些情绪模式的存在。从音乐上来说，它具有黑暗和复杂性，反映了我们所有人在自己的脑海中所经历的一切。这首歌是关于接受那些你不知道该怎么办的强烈感受。” </p><p><iframe title="WILLOW - 大感觉（官方展示台）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AfGPYMgj4-8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>由 Willow 本人执导，这首歌的伴奏视觉效果显示她站在带有黄色和绿色圆圈的黑色背景前。在整个视频中，威利奥穿着浅蓝色西装外套、几何辫子和金色格栅，同时笑着、摆姿势并盯着镜头。</p><p> 《Big Feelings》是即将发行的第六张录音室专辑《Empathogen》中的第二首歌曲，该专辑定于 5 月 3 日发行，<a href="https://willow.lnk.to/empathogen" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可供预订/预保存</a>。该曲目紧随主打单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/willow-returns-with-mysterious-new-single-symptom-of-life-3600216">Symptom Of Life</a> ”之后。</p><p>在《Empathogen》中，Willow 将与<a href="/artists/Jon-Batiste">Jon Batiste</a>合作制作《Home》，以及与<a href="/artists/St-Vincent">St. Vincent</a>合作制作《Pain For Fun》。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5i-wSarLIp/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-