tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两个唱片公司，Alcopop！和 Big Scary Monsters 已确认他们将加入抵制<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/the-great-escape">《大逃亡》</a>的行列，因为它与巴克莱银行有关系。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="71" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-10-best-new-artists-the-great-escape-2023-radar-3443679"><b>我们在 2023 年《大逃亡》中看到的 10 个最佳新表演</b></a></li></ul><p>总部位于布莱顿的节日由该银行赞助，该银行因对向以色列供应武器的公司进行金融投资而在加沙当前事件中引起争议。</p><p>这个问题首先由发起人 How to Catch a Pig 和 The Menstrual Cramps 乐队发起的请愿书引起关注，此后得到了包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">Alfie Templeman</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lip-critic">Lip Critic</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">Mary in the Junkyard</a>在内的艺术家的签名。敦促电影节放弃巴克莱银行作为赞助商。最初预定参加演出的 440 支乐队中，共有 208 支乐队签署了请愿书，总共有 977 名签名者。</p><p>上面写道：“参与以色列种族灭绝的银行在《大逃亡》中没有地位，《大逃亡》是独立音乐界的固定节目，在行业中享有宝贵的地位。我们拒绝让音乐被用来粉饰侵犯人权行为。我们不能让我们的创意成果成为烟幕弹，在背后投入金钱来谋杀巴勒斯坦人。” <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5aXJrJnkeRTpEfdVgUvNYs6i4F_a8JzO6-yRuINlsqgwkVQ/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请愿书可以在这里找到</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5n6txuIANC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 56